    slug: "top-things-to-do-istanbul",
    title: "Top Things to Do in Istanbul (2026)",
    metaDescription: "Discover the top things to do in Istanbul in 2026. From Hagia Sophia to Bosphorus cruises, explore the must-see attractions and experiences of a lifetime.",
    excerpt: "From ancient mosques and bustling bazaars to Bosphorus cruises and Turkish baths — here are the top things to do in Istanbul for an unforgettable trip.",
    category: "istanbul",
    date: "2025-12-06",
    dateModified: "2026-03-24",
