        proTip: "Request your DJ or playlist to build gradually: ambient lounge music during boarding and dinner, transitioning to upbeat tracks as the sun sets, and peak energy dance music for the final hour. This arc matches the natural rhythm of the cruise and keeps guests engaged throughout."
